Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,殘餘的野心 大蛇丸的陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡的氣味在這裏斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之只能先找找看了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師 你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺得住…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 水木那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師…你的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 這點小傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…全身有點…痛而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷得不是很重 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼的 氣氛有些凝重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們倆的關係不太平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我的感覺來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把狗爪子伸出來幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 好好看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小指 小指啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小指（在日語裏 小指代指女朋友）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她是伊魯卡老師的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我的感覺來說 他倆有這個嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下 這位是小椿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是水木的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚妻 水木的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 他們是清白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就是你無中生有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木給你們幾位添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道水木脫逃的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他曾在我那兒落腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻就察覺了 想要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可最後還是讓他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從當時的情況來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是無可奈何的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 當時我的阻止應該更堅決些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡 鳴人 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你們帶我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我的請求會令你們為難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無論如何也要阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小椿您的感受我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很抱歉 我不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 我們必須儘快找到水木
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小椿跟著 我們會畏手畏腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我能助您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概知道他要去什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 椿姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在逃亡的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會殺光所有追捕人員的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是耽擱了 一切就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請帶上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.00,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於奈良23號那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白根草和虎耳草給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守被幹掉了 有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 奈良家的研究所被人襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良家剛剛呈報的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據報 犯人的體態特徵與水木一致
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人那傢伙在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過虧他能想到那裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏藥材豐富並藏於深山之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警備比較薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那被盜走的都是什麼藥材7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧藥材的管理很規範
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就整理出了失竊的藥材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然與這個一致
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個中忍拿到這些又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不識破對方的目標就無從下手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然從材料上看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但或許有什麼特別的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配方的比重啦 調和的順序啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這方向沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就朝著這個方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小椿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說“要是耽擱了一切就晚了”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那傢伙的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然並不是非常瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿姐姐 快告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前他說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要得到大蛇丸的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到他身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想奪走封印之書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了送給大蛇丸做見面禮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小椿 你居然知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒對村裏人說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶走封印之書 這已經是重罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到他真正的目的 就會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他能改邪歸正
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你也會因為包庇而被罰的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已做好思想準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道水木的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始你一人去追就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也許無法阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能看他在罪惡中越陷越深
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做出這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸那傢伙  原來你的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這調和方法 那些忍者能模仿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是專業人士才能搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不會客
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人越獄事件的處理報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 進來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 除去水木 風神 雷神三人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘犯人全部追捕歸案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 我們正在展開那三人的搜尋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最後抓捕的犯人\N說了些令人擔心的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人擔心的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是看到三人一起逃跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風神雷神和水木一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們三個真的在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派出的那些人必敗無疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說鹿丸  這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠糟的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸 查克拉已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以我才在想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果放開這兩個傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就自身難保了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些無禮的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前也只能先牽制住他們來保全自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們活著回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個傢伙真是體力驚人的怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下 他們一身贅肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實都是肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以爆發力應該很驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只剩下這個辦法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 大夥們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了 水木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 他已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能奮戰在戰場的傢伙只會拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是輕傷 不過總歸是傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 被幻術束縛了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是…大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼已經行蹤不明的你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你倒是讓我看到了很有意思的一幕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你殺了受傷的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於把村子視為家庭的木葉忍者而言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是很少見的光景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒做錯 我別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個性急的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有責備你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是為了任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村會有承認你的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我送你的見面禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是心意轉變了 就到那裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我是第一個造訪這裏的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右數第八塊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸的力量究竟是怎樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是什麼時侯見過大蛇丸我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但答案一定就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次封印之書的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你一定很惱火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那件事已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當場就報過仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那傢伙和大蛇丸有牽連的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要問他一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我必須要找到那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在前邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下萬事俱備了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙似乎在搗什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種讓人毛骨悚然的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你們這群糾纏不清的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也正打算和你們好好幹一場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木 你的野心到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的嘴永遠都這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子總是如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為我的第一批獵物 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們的榮幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…簡直就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 你很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸的…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水木
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫最強的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你想得到多麼強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些靠藥物得來的力量都是虛假的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.10,0:22:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大蛇丸調配的藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將你和那東西一起打倒 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:22:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因緣的對決 你是打敗不了我的
